This directory contains the following subdirectories:
  SPARC  contains the Sun-SPARC version.
  MacII  contains the Apple-Macintosh-II version.
  DECstation  contains the DECstation version.
  RS6000  contains the IBM RS/6000 version.
  Windows contains the Windows 3.1 and Windows NT version for Intel 386
  SiliconGraphics  contains the SGI version.
  HP700 contains the version for HP Apollo Serie 700
  Docu  contains general Oberon documentation (not related to
        a particular implementation) as compressed postscript files.
  Tools  contains various tools for Oberon in source form.

See the readme files in the appropriate subdirectory for
further important notes.
For technical reports of the Institut fuer Computersysteme
contact Mr. Ruettener (e-mail: ruettener@inf.ethz.ch).


